div.data-content:
圆柱体的位置

$$
\begin{cases}
x_1 &= u_2 - (R-r) \sin u_1 \\
y_1 &= (R-r) \cos u_1
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{cases}
v_{x_1} &= \dot x_1 = \dot u_2 - (R-r) \dot u_1 \cos u_1 \\
v_{y_1} &= \dot y_1 = - (R-r)\dot u_1 \sin u_1
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
考虑接触点, 由坐标系转化

$$\vec v_1 + \vec {r \theta} = \vec u_2$$

可得

$$\vec {r \theta} = \left ( -(R-r) \cos u_1, -(R-r) \sin u_1 \right) = -\vec {(R-r) u_1}$$

所以

$$\theta = -\frac{R-r}{r} u_1$$

div.data-content:
圆柱体的动能

$$
\begin{alignat}{2}
&\text{平动:} T_r &&= \frac{1}{2} m_1 \left ( (\dot u_2 -
(R - r) \dot u_1 \cos u_1 )^2 + ((R - r) \dot u_1 \cos u_1 )^2\right)\\
&\text{转动:} T_r &&= \frac{1}{2} J \dot \theta^2 \\
&&&= \frac{1}{2}(\frac{1}{2} m r^2) \dot (\frac {R-r}{r}u_1)^2
\end{alignat}
$$
